{"tid":1332200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有片有圖 求蓮花圖 有巿民深水埗區議會叫囂民建聯鄭泳舜每月收十萬破壞社會安寧","createTime":"2019-07-19T08:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T04:27:56.000Z","uid":113000,"like":40,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9d42c65d612e24e1e68e6e7bb58faf3589e916a0","tid":1332200,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:26:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552919/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552919%2F&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMV8wxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=02b82b49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F552919%2F&h=440fd914\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/552919/</a><br />\n<br />\n深水埗區議會會議因叫囂提早結束<br />\n更新：2019/07/19 14:14<br />\n深水埗區議會早上開會，約三十名市民到場旁聽，多次高叫「嚴懲暴徒」等口號，令會議三度暫停，最終提早結束。 <br />\n<br />\n早上九時半開會，深水埗區議會主席張永森一開始講解會議流程，有旁聽的市民叫囂。這日的議程，除了討論增建醫院等民生議題，亦包括討論行政長官就修例事件的回應，以及成立獨立調查委員會等，張永森多次要求在場人士肅靜。一復會，主席邀請屋宇署署長就座，有人再叫囂，主席其後兩度宣佈休會，到大約十時半，改由副主席陳偉明主持會議。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n會議結束後，有區議員與市民發生口角，有人報警，警員到場調停，民主派區議員表示會去信主席，希望未來一星期重開會議。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JkRQg44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJkRQg44.png&h=7a86e176&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WyGgW45.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWyGgW45.png&h=8fa827c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tFYqYq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tFYqYq.png&h=fef4b28f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iHkp5Yr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiHkp5Yr.png&h=f49a3c20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B1d3B43.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB1d3B43.png&h=2a17d387&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c619dfa5307a50e77ebb15ffcce1f09f88a7724f","tid":1332200,"uid":238051,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:27:20.000Z","msg":"【有人冒警】面對冒警情境練習場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1332100\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1332100</a><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">有人冒警\n你扮警察\n冇委任證\n涉嫌傷人\n藏有攻擊性武器\n我地行使公民逮捕權</code></pre>"},{"pid":"c18d91d6d89c9384c09910c5d081e5a9e8eaee98","tid":1332200,"uid":113000,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"有埋個阿姐大頭蓮花圖更好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f628b2c216d65d32905cf9ce2e84944a6f448d8f","tid":1332200,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b84684a567b045e27b372bc705c8c50527196f7","tid":1332200,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:37:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43feebe45840d73ee8b76bd460cbe8d9d0325226","tid":1332200,"uid":403,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"深水埗市民到該區區議會怒斥民建聯每月收十幾萬破壞社會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91a847cebec376ea6689945270ba12b9c3b6542","tid":1332200,"uid":159920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0fb29bf9db213097cab88974403c6201a4ee903b","tid":1332200,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"43feebe45840d73ee8b76bd460cbe8d9d0325226","tid":1332200,"uid":403,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:39:47.000Z","msg":"深水埗市民到該區區議會怒斥民建聯每月收十幾萬破壞社會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:43:20.000Z"